Thank you.

766
00:46:45.420 --> 00:46:48.482
Hey. are you crying?

767
00:46:48.506 --> 00:46:50.940
No.

768
00:46:57.849 --> 00:47:00.894
I'm sorry. You're not
supposed to see me like this.

769
00:47:00.918 --> 00:47:03.252
No. it's okay. Really.

770
00:47:04.489 --> 00:47:06.383
Uh. what's the matter?

771
00:47:06.407 --> 00:47:08.240
It's Steve.

772
00:47:09.576 --> 00:47:12.136
He's not the man
I thought he was.

773
00:47:13.665 --> 00:47:16.844
Sarah. your husband
is a great man.

774
00:47:16.868 --> 00:47:21.998
And I feel bad about
what we did last night too.

775
00:47:22.022 --> 00:47:25.035
But we can't try to make
it easier on ourselves by...

776
00:47:25.059 --> 00:47:26.854
By blaming the victim.

777
00:47:26.878 --> 00:47:29.923
Jason.

778
00:47:29.947 --> 00:47:33.393
you and Luke and all the others.

779
00:47:33.417 --> 00:47:35.777
you're not being
trained to defend us.

780
00:47:37.505 --> 00:47:41.435
He wants to use
you to start a war.

781
00:47:41.459 --> 00:47:44.310
Does that sound like
a great man to you?

782
00:47:46.047 --> 00:47:48.847
What? Well. he's not one.

783
00:47:49.951 --> 00:47:51.128
And I thought he was.

784
00:47:51.152 --> 00:47:54.965
but lately I've been
seeing a side of him

785
00:47:54.989 --> 00:47:58.234
I never did before.

786
00:47:58.258 --> 00:48:02.561
He's vicious and he's cruel.
and he uses the C-word.

787
00:48:04.532 --> 00:48:07.027
And he lies to me. Jason.

788
00:48:07.051 --> 00:48:08.996
Our marriage has
always been a partnership.

789
00:48:09.020 --> 00:48:11.448
but now he's shutting me out.

790
00:48:11.472 --> 00:48:13.149
Uh...

791
00:48:13.173 --> 00:48:16.070
Come on. now. Here.

792
00:48:16.094 --> 00:48:17.893
Don't cry.

793
00:48:20.565 --> 00:48:22.948
There. All gone.

794
00:48:28.706 --> 00:48:31.185
Whoa. whoa. whoa.

795
00:48:31.209 --> 00:48:32.919
I should go.

796
00:48:32.943 --> 00:48:36.256
When I was a little girl.

797
00:48:36.280 --> 00:48:38.525
I realized that I had a calling.

798
00:48:38.549 --> 00:48:39.927
Uh-huh.

799
00:48:39.951 --> 00:48:41.828
That I was put
here on this earth

800
00:48:41.852 --> 00:48:44.265
to be that great woman
behind her great man.

801
00:48:44.289 --> 00:48:46.433
And when Steve
came into my life.

802
00:48:46.457 --> 00:48:48.640
I thought he was that man.

803
00:48:50.511 --> 00:48:52.990
But now I see it.

804
00:48:53.014 --> 00:48:55.214
clear as day.

805
00:48:56.550 --> 00:48:58.801
I'm supposed to be with you.

806
00:49:00.287 --> 00:49:02.687
Hey. hey. whoa. whoa. whoa.

807
00:49:03.791 --> 00:49:06.008
We can't. It's wrong.

808
00:49:08.262 --> 00:49:10.596
You're married. Not in my heart.

809
00:49:12.116 --> 00:49:14.360
Not anymore.

810
00:49:14.384 --> 00:49:16.931
And how can this be wrong

811
00:49:16.955 --> 00:49:20.555
if it's what God's
commanding me to do?

812
00:49:23.861 --> 00:49:27.562
Think God really wants this?

813
00:49:28.966 --> 00:49:30.666
Yes.

814
00:49:34.772 --> 00:49:36.917
You talk to him?

815
00:49:36.941 --> 00:49:40.008
Every single day of my life.

816
00:49:41.679 --> 00:49:44.224
And he wants this. Jason.

817
00:49:44.248 --> 00:49:48.250
Oh. God. I promise.

818
00:49:57.094 --> 00:49:58.694
Okay.

819
00:50:19.667 --> 00:50:20.977
Where are you taking me?

820
00:50:21.001 --> 00:50:22.780
Don't be such a nervous nelly.

821
00:50:22.804 --> 00:50:24.870
It's a surprise.

822
00:50:33.364 --> 00:50:36.109
What? You don't like drums?

823
00:50:36.133 --> 00:50:39.496
No. It's just that
in my experience.

824
00:50:39.520 --> 00:50:41.815
no good can come
from drum music.

825
00:50:41.839 --> 00:50:44.768
Follow it and all it ever leads
you to is hippies and cults.

826
00:50:44.792 --> 00:50:46.425
Not this time.

827
00:50:48.212 --> 00:50:51.859
Whoa! Hey! Unh!

828
00:50:51.883 --> 00:50:52.943
Daphne?

829
00:50:52.967 --> 00:50:55.512
Sorry. Sam.

830
00:50:55.536 --> 00:50:57.031
What the hell's going on?

831
00:51:20.361 --> 00:51:22.473
What the fuck is this?

832
00:51:22.497 --> 00:51:24.730
It's the end of the road.

833
00:51:59.834 --> 00:52:03.881
No! No!

833
